Microsoft Edge Enterprise Management (EPM) — Evaluation Report
Evaluated by: Pallavi | Date: July 2026

EPM was evaluated against our organisation's browser and password management requirements using a hands-on approach in the company's live environment with global admin and Edge admin access.

EPM Feature Assessment

Feature, Status, Notes
Password Storage and Autofill, Tested, Saves and autofills passwords
Password Monitor, Tested, Detects leaked reused and weak passwords
Azure AD SSO, Tested, Sign-in on Microsoft and non-Microsoft apps
Extension Monitoring, Tested, 30 extensions visible with user counts
Secure Password Deployment, Testing in Progress, Policy deployed autofill verification pending
Password Age Tracking, Not Available, EPM does not show password age
90-Day Expiry Alerts, Not Available, No built-in notification in EPM
